{"id": "nat_0", "text": "The birch canoe slid on the smooth planks.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": 4.268282890319824, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.290840965536014, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5448948473786115, "dnsmos_bak": 4.108618577535767}
{"id": "nat_1", "text": "Glue the sheet to the dark blue background.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.311861515045166, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3259649165908094, "dnsmos_sig": 3.591341165102985, "dnsmos_bak": 4.130006471171602}
{"id": "nat_2", "text": "It is easy to tell the depth of a well.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": 4.213464736938477, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.349791541708327, "dnsmos_sig": 3.577501501899961, "dnsmos_bak": 4.185342349990018}
{"id": "nat_3", "text": "These days a chicken leg is a rare dish.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.421441555023193, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3702784730060134, "dnsmos_sig": 3.601881032741115, "dnsmos_bak": 4.082902275675487}
{"id": "nat_4", "text": "Rice is often served in round bowls.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": 4.259977340698242, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.270184015531655, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6175085023688553, "dnsmos_bak": 3.914936481603826}
{"id": "nat_5", "text": "The juice of lemons makes fine punch.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.359612464904785, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.30373175560711, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5547436835483532, "dnsmos_bak": 4.10642567692301}
{"id": "nat_6", "text": "The box was thrown beside the parked truck.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 3.51479172706604, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9656545850258835, "dnsmos_sig": 3.263199284543686, "dnsmos_bak": 3.964143220526141}
{"id": "nat_7", "text": "The hogs were fed chopped corn and garbage.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": 3.825819969177246, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3095467929713545, "dnsmos_sig": 3.547166369762936, "dnsmos_bak": 4.143142720239795}
{"id": "nat_8", "text": "Four hours of steady work faced us.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.318501949310303, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.335921634904461, "dnsmos_sig": 3.583809530253668, "dnsmos_bak": 4.121200876774531}
{"id": "nat_9", "text": "Large size in stockings is hard to sell.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.369147777557373, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3704411023423537, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6201663983427297, "dnsmos_bak": 4.146016912071892}
{"id": "nat_10", "text": "The boy was there when the sun rose.", "audio_duration_s": 1.6718367346938776, "utmos": 4.086636543273926, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0966182261901247, "dnsmos_sig": 3.445663302448955, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9092358516168595}
{"id": "nat_11", "text": "A rod is used to catch pink salmon.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 3.973078489303589, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.358882521722843, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5912428645676586, "dnsmos_bak": 4.169923312753211}
{"id": "nat_12", "text": "The source of the huge river is the clear spring.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": 4.3417134284973145, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.409453782367823, "dnsmos_sig": 3.648915659108602, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1498466075633464}
{"id": "nat_13", "text": "Kick the ball straight and follow through.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.20728063583374, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2936977416370232, "dnsmos_sig": 3.587521971888561, "dnsmos_bak": 4.068229279752171}
{"id": "nat_14", "text": "Help the woman get back to her feet.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 4.142228126525879, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.302543599667601, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5335589940553676, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1786873205880095}
{"id": "nat_15", "text": "A blue crane is a tall wading bird.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": 3.922632932662964, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2529240110330653, "dnsmos_sig": 3.559523257402016, "dnsmos_bak": 4.000263450666828}
{"id": "nat_16", "text": "It is hard to erase blue or red ink.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.128406524658203, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.060165601018386, "dnsmos_sig": 3.392353277183064, "dnsmos_bak": 3.980149183134614}
{"id": "nat_17", "text": "Write quickly and meet me at the dock.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 4.167452335357666, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.113444611709276, "dnsmos_sig": 3.529346487646669, "dnsmos_bak": 3.859052516754157}
{"id": "nat_18", "text": "The two talked quietly in the dim light.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.203908443450928, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.17357570841201, "dnsmos_sig": 3.491537517908102, "dnsmos_bak": 4.001783380412386}
{"id": "nat_19", "text": "The hail pattered on the burnt red tiles.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": 4.07797908782959, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.333956200205101, "dnsmos_sig": 3.60087334214943, "dnsmos_bak": 4.107788517715198}
{"id": "nat_20", "text": "The sand drifted down the steep slope.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.323817729949951, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0948642481869535, "dnsmos_sig": 3.438048529518516, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9483586381800158}
{"id": "nat_21", "text": "Oak is strong and also gives shade.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 4.341529846191406, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.355288868855407, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5887380773898045, "dnsmos_bak": 4.133426441890814}
{"id": "nat_22", "text": "Cats and dogs each hate the other.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 4.025513172149658, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.247191057609504, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5074441714087548, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1169874929269925}
{"id": "nat_23", "text": "The pipe began to rust while new.", "audio_duration_s": 1.6718367346938776, "utmos": 3.9654479026794434, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4157069460452005, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6635946882408494, "dnsmos_bak": 4.163607594878582}
{"id": "nat_24", "text": "Open the crate but don't break the glass.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 3.6548948287963867, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4352212032964755, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6747530047582866, "dnsmos_bak": 4.19526920875557}
{"id": "nat_25", "text": "Add the sum to the product of these three.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 3.7340006828308105, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.188300218923685, "dnsmos_sig": 3.446633634292187, "dnsmos_bak": 4.101494373435831}
{"id": "nat_26", "text": "Thieves who rob friends deserve jail.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 4.412752151489258, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2452000238406455, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5514013654116434, "dnsmos_bak": 4.039250565615594}
{"id": "nat_27", "text": "The ripe taste of cheese improves with age.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": 4.318116188049316, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2108246439378334, "dnsmos_sig": 3.480332884393691, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0532980025866445}
{"id": "nat_28", "text": "Act on these orders with great speed.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.401798248291016, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.230678167154276, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5143166191399087, "dnsmos_bak": 4.047594979777845}
{"id": "nat_29", "text": "The hush of night came on the water.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 3.740100145339966, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.937918557854014, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5574816204059463, "dnsmos_bak": 3.5452861343494}
{"id": "nat_30", "text": "Flax makes linen for many a dress.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.2379937171936035, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.145421544768138, "dnsmos_sig": 3.561192163273482, "dnsmos_bak": 3.76056816783487}
{"id": "nat_31", "text": "Hoist the load to your left shoulder.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.0558390617370605, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.033308188543003, "dnsmos_sig": 3.502528020421451, "dnsmos_bak": 3.6795223313631893}
{"id": "nat_32", "text": "Take the winding path to reach the lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.409171104431152, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2268726315285567, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4738802409520915, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1104294439273605}
{"id": "nat_33", "text": "Note closely the size of the gas tank.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.291271686553955, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.180476171292415, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4986439496286224, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9984596981655574}
{"id": "nat_34", "text": "Wipe the grease off his dirty face.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.1769304275512695, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.029937185696185, "dnsmos_sig": 3.442788438771494, "dnsmos_bak": 3.7549623021213443}
{"id": "nat_35", "text": "Mend the coat before wearing it again.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 3.431842803955078, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3401386194687355, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5754630812200126, "dnsmos_bak": 4.149102145864754}
{"id": "nat_36", "text": "The lease ran out in sixteen weeks.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.450711727142334, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3440918870943017, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6014384701204714, "dnsmos_bak": 4.120208394644592}
{"id": "nat_37", "text": "Both parts of the design came together.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.1648149490356445, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2411358810500808, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4731511723973063, "dnsmos_bak": 4.139497414695744}
{"id": "nat_38", "text": "Sewing hems and darns takes skill.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 3.9094200134277344, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2599953037145233, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5152686336249017, "dnsmos_bak": 4.089851936158864}
{"id": "nat_39", "text": "The architect planned a new city hall.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.151765823364258, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3434925756141385, "dnsmos_sig": 3.58678346030262, "dnsmos_bak": 4.113091267602669}
{"id": "nat_40", "text": "The small red lamp stood in a corner.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.341930866241455, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.296955025832933, "dnsmos_sig": 3.563334838940704, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1268907692875985}
{"id": "nat_41", "text": "The large box came by truck to town.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.316901206970215, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4422174302474375, "dnsmos_sig": 3.66567380545045, "dnsmos_bak": 4.221084086369172}
{"id": "nat_42", "text": "The men fought hard to save the fort.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 4.352144241333008, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3346664366222436, "dnsmos_sig": 3.594756456868325, "dnsmos_bak": 4.137559407542108}
{"id": "nat_43", "text": "The horse chewed his bit and nodded.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.334551811218262, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0989221244674137, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3942773429438984, "dnsmos_bak": 3.986504111903029}
{"id": "nat_44", "text": "Three of the men were hurt badly.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7182766439909296, "utmos": 4.275821685791016, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.304736746015984, "dnsmos_sig": 3.567865639346094, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1001196083815445}
{"id": "nat_45", "text": "Ripe pears are fit for a queen's table.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.299103736877441, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.300208724435826, "dnsmos_sig": 3.591159886588852, "dnsmos_bak": 4.10380282721071}
{"id": "nat_46", "text": "The dark room was lit by a red light.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 3.8566842079162598, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.162160861526758, "dnsmos_sig": 3.489354012641291, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9825337805541063}
{"id": "nat_47", "text": "The fox hid in the tall grass nearby.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 3.606337785720825, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.281076060912875, "dnsmos_sig": 3.580986713508103, "dnsmos_bak": 4.025466947174558}
{"id": "nat_48", "text": "We saw eight tiny goats on the hillside.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.250153541564941, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3168259545245773, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5937542473666046, "dnsmos_bak": 4.095021608655638}
{"id": "nat_49", "text": "The cats purred softly on the warm rug.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.194432258605957, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2712743236457946, "dnsmos_sig": 3.549406546810141, "dnsmos_bak": 4.062867239134653}
{"id": "nat_50", "text": "The silver bell rang at dawn.", "audio_duration_s": 1.5789569160997732, "utmos": 4.287371635437012, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4501217329675975, "dnsmos_sig": 3.672615417681571, "dnsmos_bak": 4.179367140743392}
{"id": "nat_51", "text": "The crowd cheered the band with pride.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.3162689208984375, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.306755283859124, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5680057933853675, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1293147385993025}
{"id": "nat_52", "text": "She baked fresh bread every morning.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7182766439909296, "utmos": 4.318766117095947, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.241105834515757, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5070292207003804, "dnsmos_bak": 4.125695495083795}
{"id": "nat_53", "text": "The train reached the bridge at noon.", "audio_duration_s": 1.6253968253968254, "utmos": 4.219497203826904, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.373688717126544, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6208455449072883, "dnsmos_bak": 4.137285886899271}
{"id": "nat_54", "text": "Cool winds blew from the distant peaks.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.330929756164551, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3107722736030776, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5707080180464468, "dnsmos_bak": 4.091310414548726}
{"id": "nat_55", "text": "The old dog slept by the warm fire.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 3.9114949703216553, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0980248344826307, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3822756395400266, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9979210201751476}
{"id": "nat_56", "text": "Bright stars filled the clear night sky.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.245217323303223, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4082231719967635, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6240162655946415, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1807697867082165}
{"id": "nat_57", "text": "The child built a castle in the sand.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.171726226806641, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3948951990723253, "dnsmos_sig": 3.649889832361945, "dnsmos_bak": 4.104920043008234}
{"id": "nat_58", "text": "Rain soaked the dry and barren plain.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": 4.3095703125, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3888693064254745, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6364053863546686, "dnsmos_bak": 4.155161261064417}
{"id": "nat_59", "text": "The boat moved quietly past the shore.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.188831329345703, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.139688659758029, "dnsmos_sig": 3.414850665644623, "dnsmos_bak": 4.061010325382562}
{"id": "nat_60", "text": "Plums ripen in the warm summer sun.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 4.165566921234131, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.19803810143436, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5113478257987296, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9748827100422126}
{"id": "nat_61", "text": "The lock was jammed but opened at last.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 3.9877140522003174, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1628275792432103, "dnsmos_sig": 3.479963090050138, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9883618711390243}
{"id": "nat_62", "text": "The key to the cabinet was misplaced.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": 4.208152770996094, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.036394688191512, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4458147282199385, "dnsmos_bak": 3.843748724585324}
{"id": "nat_63", "text": "The cup shattered on the stone floor.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 3.8803224563598633, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3586433584814985, "dnsmos_sig": 3.585106791758668, "dnsmos_bak": 4.140615584814478}
{"id": "nat_64", "text": "A black bear crossed the narrow trail.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.143182754516602, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.256526743048923, "dnsmos_sig": 3.531836177991699, "dnsmos_bak": 4.122335055498687}
{"id": "nat_65", "text": "Fresh dew glistened on the green leaves.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.316774845123291, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9350710774900093, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4282586613981594, "dnsmos_bak": 3.5242364119518883}
{"id": "nat_66", "text": "The lamp cast a soft glow on the table.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.30872106552124, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3655259795089485, "dnsmos_sig": 3.586558248749929, "dnsmos_bak": 4.165711147055618}
{"id": "nat_67", "text": "Strong winds bent the tall pine trees.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": 4.403409957885742, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3440364548393346, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5831831499685745, "dnsmos_bak": 4.111246973164072}
{"id": "nat_68", "text": "A robin sang from the old oak branch.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": 4.331645488739014, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3761860773847028, "dnsmos_sig": 3.622468174667908, "dnsmos_bak": 4.10176932478315}
{"id": "nat_69", "text": "The crowd fell silent when he spoke.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.208340644836426, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3910449144319954, "dnsmos_sig": 3.635142127454833, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1591349648920914}
{"id": "nat_70", "text": "Green fields stretched to the far horizon.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": 3.8426473140716553, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2771953583577953, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5647549806810863, "dnsmos_bak": 4.080840173516252}
{"id": "nat_71", "text": "The river ran swift and cold today.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.313207626342773, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.316622910462506, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5747421533423993, "dnsmos_bak": 4.120468730204892}
{"id": "nat_72", "text": "The flag waved high in the morning breeze.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": 4.27977180480957, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3547160837666645, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6103346888462604, "dnsmos_bak": 4.133348589879708}
{"id": "nat_73", "text": "Blue jays flew low over the meadow.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 4.076615810394287, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1607637016062973, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4748224856167966, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9707614071451434}
{"id": "nat_74", "text": "The forge was lit at break of day.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 4.234267234802246, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.301095676735582, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5706059487189514, "dnsmos_bak": 4.127038495937359}
{"id": "nat_75", "text": "The sparrows hopped on the garden wall.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 3.895932197570801, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4472484097628686, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6918421720821506, "dnsmos_bak": 4.164871354279358}
{"id": "nat_76", "text": "Fill the car before you drive into town.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.140259742736816, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1237548213996607, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5156325229106735, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8809424377447796}
{"id": "nat_77", "text": "A cud of grass hung from the heifer's lip.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.224264144897461, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.487103271392996, "dnsmos_sig": 3.7265123035899275, "dnsmos_bak": 4.178483693759511}
{"id": "nat_78", "text": "The seed grew into a giant oak tree.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": 4.426821708679199, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1826440845063324, "dnsmos_sig": 3.520675901187904, "dnsmos_bak": 3.965155287146816}
{"id": "nat_79", "text": "A worm ate through the wooden plank.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 3.923312187194824, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1832560889953823, "dnsmos_sig": 3.599337870608473, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8962743486850324}
{"id": "nat_80", "text": "The team scored in the last few seconds.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.006937026977539, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3520594708484963, "dnsmos_sig": 3.593651053226328, "dnsmos_bak": 4.115206982138901}
{"id": "nat_81", "text": "The glass jar held the bright red jam.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.254023551940918, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.353256157587887, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6102035591445305, "dnsmos_bak": 4.150537765021491}
{"id": "nat_82", "text": "The leaves fell slowly in the autumn air.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.252053260803223, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.927793971961883, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3746837239810894, "dnsmos_bak": 3.695743056058174}
{"id": "nat_83", "text": "The farmer planted seeds in long rows.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.090270042419434, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3373872335472337, "dnsmos_sig": 3.578237028348724, "dnsmos_bak": 4.150248854092079}
{"id": "nat_84", "text": "The clock struck twelve at midnight.", "audio_duration_s": 1.6718367346938776, "utmos": 4.277161598205566, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.271546629183012, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5471547859314416, "dnsmos_bak": 4.104884836268716}
{"id": "nat_85", "text": "A pale moon rose over the distant hills.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": 3.8767495155334473, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.430419357357121, "dnsmos_sig": 3.643381945017585, "dnsmos_bak": 4.205734489903989}
{"id": "nat_86", "text": "The stream carved a path through the stone.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.148435592651367, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.385871996668261, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6389930293089523, "dnsmos_bak": 4.141536349277375}
{"id": "nat_87", "text": "Bright flowers bloomed along the fence.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.0067291259765625, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2316872903733977, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5426010187506844, "dnsmos_bak": 3.993674247993577}
{"id": "nat_88", "text": "The snow lay deep on the mountain pass.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 3.922067642211914, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.317098377655932, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5987170337013508, "dnsmos_bak": 4.105769275930443}
{"id": "nat_89", "text": "The eagle soared above the canyon rim.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.0087666511535645, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.297375839448255, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5892546169018593, "dnsmos_bak": 4.041550329524103}
{"id": "nat_90", "text": "The gate swung open with a loud creak.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.246960639953613, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.19807357019398, "dnsmos_sig": 3.467655217326472, "dnsmos_bak": 4.097209516189866}
{"id": "nat_91", "text": "The wolf howled at the cold winter moon.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 3.9558231830596924, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2027955060803803, "dnsmos_sig": 3.565523044794181, "dnsmos_bak": 3.891378347561833}
{"id": "nat_92", "text": "A candle flickered in the draft of wind.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.3409647941589355, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4265328854595616, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6654143008412747, "dnsmos_bak": 4.174052889965785}
{"id": "nat_93", "text": "The road curved sharply past the barn.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.323788642883301, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.426815846458116, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6495432443064764, "dnsmos_bak": 4.178186538658928}
{"id": "nat_94", "text": "Wool is spun into yarn for warm cloth.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.338348388671875, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.327148080108199, "dnsmos_sig": 3.631362285296066, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0835863329863695}
{"id": "nat_95", "text": "The crowd surged through the narrow gate.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.296182632446289, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.206700552190811, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4917988967780844, "dnsmos_bak": 4.049183218388679}
{"id": "nat_96", "text": "The owl hunted mice in the dark field.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.024608135223389, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2002014612524263, "dnsmos_sig": 3.521919671811109, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9694098761112615}
{"id": "nat_97", "text": "The pond froze solid in January.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.338959693908691, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2806223578005698, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5800939997572105, "dnsmos_bak": 4.058822692822035}
{"id": "nat_98", "text": "A flock of geese flew in a V-shape.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 3.893096923828125, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.933300749346878, "dnsmos_sig": 3.278575950324426, "dnsmos_bak": 3.823905903740876}
{"id": "nat_99", "text": "The tide ebbed low on the rocky coast.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 3.8644113540649414, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3293716111455818, "dnsmos_sig": 3.621955120707951, "dnsmos_bak": 4.048363759055771}
{"id": "nat_100", "text": "The flame burned bright in the dark cave.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.272279262542725, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.26749437990588, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5544682908311365, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0387173275140205}
{"id": "nat_101", "text": "The mill ground grain into fine flour.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.3231201171875, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.404448126428495, "dnsmos_sig": 3.639178258972355, "dnsmos_bak": 4.177674113815894}
{"id": "nat_102", "text": "The stag grazed near the edge of the wood.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 3.967927932739258, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.9068471608012367, "dnsmos_sig": 3.3424786998591167, "dnsmos_bak": 3.662001137333443}
{"id": "nat_103", "text": "The well dried up in the hot summer.", "audio_duration_s": 1.6253968253968254, "utmos": 4.2893877029418945, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2071698593317794, "dnsmos_sig": 3.49405592864927, "dnsmos_bak": 4.055943959790186}
{"id": "nat_104", "text": "The swift brown fox ran past the log.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": 4.161045074462891, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.280275179367977, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5296157282730154, "dnsmos_bak": 4.143473382390288}
{"id": "nat_105", "text": "A stone wall bordered the old estate.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.005903720855713, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2335392155955867, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5430855388149545, "dnsmos_bak": 4.063882612150905}
{"id": "nat_106", "text": "The bell rang twice before it stopped.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.28115701675415, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.289118222902347, "dnsmos_sig": 3.544209874416545, "dnsmos_bak": 4.143554673507813}
{"id": "nat_107", "text": "The hawk soared high on the warm updraft.", "audio_duration_s": 2.414875283446712, "utmos": 4.314349174499512, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2832962692745764, "dnsmos_sig": 3.54500245699417, "dnsmos_bak": 4.089808897462689}
{"id": "nat_108", "text": "The sharp knife cut the rough cord.", "audio_duration_s": 1.6718367346938776, "utmos": 4.220247268676758, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.302913128969171, "dnsmos_sig": 3.545556892682024, "dnsmos_bak": 4.150669171167976}
{"id": "nat_109", "text": "The colt pranced in the wide green field.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.327392578125, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.369147948633827, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6365407622004433, "dnsmos_bak": 4.147607092427279}
{"id": "nat_110", "text": "A fish leaped from the calm blue lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 3.869546413421631, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.289094298126113, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5415411433768287, "dnsmos_bak": 4.125400431687129}
{"id": "nat_111", "text": "The damp ground smelled of fresh rain.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.21783447265625, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.313663967609284, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5840429940389815, "dnsmos_bak": 4.115097221250688}
{"id": "nat_112", "text": "The cart was loaded with heavy stone.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.213108539581299, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.247233665269516, "dnsmos_sig": 3.538923897358538, "dnsmos_bak": 4.072779058810221}
{"id": "nat_113", "text": "The long white rope coiled on the deck.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 3.452244281768799, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.12254816134098, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4587076103438528, "dnsmos_bak": 3.941739079583886}
{"id": "nat_114", "text": "The pine tree grew tall and straight.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.251683712005615, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2172307627132546, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4854873633369734, "dnsmos_bak": 4.106005022087676}
{"id": "nat_115", "text": "The coal burned slowly in the iron stove.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": 4.191488265991211, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3581974087662867, "dnsmos_sig": 3.632743848106541, "dnsmos_bak": 4.060632583123764}
{"id": "nat_116", "text": "A gust of wind tore the sail apart.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 3.7007956504821777, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2620967421881, "dnsmos_sig": 3.548156738114496, "dnsmos_bak": 4.068628426768397}
{"id": "nat_117", "text": "The goat climbed steep rocky paths easily.", "audio_duration_s": 2.647074829931973, "utmos": 4.423676490783691, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.399625371263761, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6402554292420106, "dnsmos_bak": 4.165809160289116}
{"id": "nat_118", "text": "The red sun sank below the flat plain.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 4.106365203857422, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.283417988107019, "dnsmos_sig": 3.561584881473601, "dnsmos_bak": 4.132250307058608}
{"id": "nat_119", "text": "The wheat field swayed in the warm breeze.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.3916425704956055, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.8826131095329193, "dnsmos_sig": 3.2189818081356845, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8058108592950104}
{"id": "nat_120", "text": "The thick fog rolled in from the sea.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 3.889075994491577, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2002532040558065, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5568238357924704, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9279855325717206}
{"id": "nat_121", "text": "The drum beat loud and steady all night.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 4.290148735046387, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0671857909849902, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4332237984128966, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9047127564466906}
{"id": "nat_122", "text": "The fox left tracks in the new snow.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.330716133117676, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3428666566287855, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5953762675004977, "dnsmos_bak": 4.179560240556573}
{"id": "nat_123", "text": "The light faded as the sun went down.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.106514930725098, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.26910763929754, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5319615137080356, "dnsmos_bak": 4.116156752631756}
{"id": "nat_124", "text": "A small boat drifted on the still lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.2664618492126465, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.169852534706949, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4741411750107085, "dnsmos_bak": 4.025142201563422}
{"id": "nat_125", "text": "The cook prepared a fresh pot of soup.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.1669921875, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2808273333485034, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5266410748231265, "dnsmos_bak": 4.106686951393205}
{"id": "nat_126", "text": "The old mill wheel turned in the stream.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 3.8279178142547607, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.282549323942376, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5937108703031986, "dnsmos_bak": 4.099708445218489}
{"id": "nat_127", "text": "The long drought burned the crops dry.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.145463466644287, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2691182279789204, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5348934711059252, "dnsmos_bak": 4.126635388609449}
{"id": "nat_128", "text": "The cool air smelled of pine and earth.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.201972007751465, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.348884358494672, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6019362190518445, "dnsmos_bak": 4.136252785005325}
{"id": "nat_129", "text": "The child ran barefoot in the wet grass.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 4.319609642028809, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.423863622759551, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6638939974588878, "dnsmos_bak": 4.148589070386469}
{"id": "nat_130", "text": "A kite soared high above the park.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 3.8084168434143066, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1644472867333557, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5051395833297647, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9847342186059986}
{"id": "nat_131", "text": "The bridge shook as the truck rolled past.", "audio_duration_s": 2.36843537414966, "utmos": 4.21492338180542, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2946955439438743, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5645120978020444, "dnsmos_bak": 4.085230400536638}
{"id": "nat_132", "text": "The soft light fell on the open book.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.146180629730225, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.903472895842212, "dnsmos_sig": 3.394780677877732, "dnsmos_bak": 3.594722870430939}
{"id": "nat_133", "text": "The crane lifted the heavy steel beam.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.355536937713623, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.280482373915763, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5210460700064607, "dnsmos_bak": 4.126271762093172}
{"id": "nat_134", "text": "The strong horse pulled the loaded cart.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.252529621124268, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3188207146144344, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5612973930332976, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1262145062691244}
{"id": "nat_135", "text": "The wind died down as night came on.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": 4.397885799407959, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.332024248112249, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6059735866274374, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0901272075028094}
{"id": "nat_136", "text": "The bird built its nest in the fork of the branch.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": 3.82131290435791, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2562643856076803, "dnsmos_sig": 3.520291648268555, "dnsmos_bak": 4.127453043379817}
{"id": "nat_137", "text": "The ice was thin near the river bank.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": 3.8824779987335205, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2683274321973883, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6286213206250837, "dnsmos_bak": 3.94288935273696}
{"id": "nat_138", "text": "The fog lifted slowly as the sun rose.", "audio_duration_s": 2.5541950113378684, "utmos": 4.204525947570801, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2949298901543593, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5581073824533194, "dnsmos_bak": 4.128022926338362}
{"id": "nat_139", "text": "The fire crackled in the stone hearth.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 3.915360927581787, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.501204732908316, "dnsmos_sig": 3.7416163418270805, "dnsmos_bak": 4.186531275998138}
{"id": "nat_140", "text": "The long bridge arched over the bay.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.286240100860596, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2702043470295257, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5159649330973104, "dnsmos_bak": 4.108493845157845}
{"id": "nat_141", "text": "A cloud of dust rose from the dry road.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.218194007873535, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.15438681542526, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5511589045467846, "dnsmos_bak": 3.919882697187661}
{"id": "nat_142", "text": "The swift stream ran over smooth stones.", "audio_duration_s": 2.461315192743764, "utmos": 4.314657211303711, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2914804843858025, "dnsmos_sig": 3.524371830406983, "dnsmos_bak": 4.126001099659352}
{"id": "nat_143", "text": "The torch cast shadows on the old wall.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2755555555555556, "utmos": 4.1273603439331055, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.463811640713164, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6873066901417335, "dnsmos_bak": 4.181385647969289}
{"id": "nat_144", "text": "The net was full of silver fish.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7182766439909296, "utmos": 4.2124857902526855, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.357012863078765, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5943610434727633, "dnsmos_bak": 4.154254400680255}
{"id": "nat_145", "text": "The tall grain stood ripe in the field.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 4.2012739181518555, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.117408260584495, "dnsmos_sig": 3.431810328015963, "dnsmos_bak": 4.017172247609558}
{"id": "nat_146", "text": "The damp cloth wiped the dusty shelf.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.248693943023682, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.294589059896886, "dnsmos_sig": 3.563817950081841, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1246523482826385}
{"id": "nat_147", "text": "A mule team pulled the heavy plow.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 3.4523837566375732, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.394399697717314, "dnsmos_sig": 3.632258920199953, "dnsmos_bak": 4.166782609324548}
{"id": "nat_148", "text": "The old chair sat in the corner unused.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.396733283996582, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.222154539460904, "dnsmos_sig": 3.54707510385594, "dnsmos_bak": 3.977754167549442}
{"id": "nat_149", "text": "The rain fell steadily through the night.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 3.9015321731567383, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.177602484438484, "dnsmos_sig": 3.483390740241186, "dnsmos_bak": 4.001235901921803}
{"id": "nat_150", "text": "The lantern hung from the low beam.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 4.2887372970581055, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.277893342959339, "dnsmos_sig": 3.636622305442567, "dnsmos_bak": 3.996021958976577}
{"id": "nat_151", "text": "The wind brought the smell of fresh hay.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 3.4123764038085938, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2495551066461488, "dnsmos_sig": 3.569604313453928, "dnsmos_bak": 4.025669967426654}
{"id": "nat_152", "text": "The stone path led to the small gate.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.258535385131836, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3030541974477376, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6086701380163793, "dnsmos_bak": 4.085629369845953}
{"id": "nat_153", "text": "The loud noise startled the sleeping dog.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.23344612121582, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2471873137982428, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5587733689178194, "dnsmos_bak": 4.024274796831338}
{"id": "nat_154", "text": "The canoe glided across the glassy lake.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.358313083648682, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.298331423006121, "dnsmos_sig": 3.570145796556119, "dnsmos_bak": 4.09705290914968}
{"id": "nat_155", "text": "The long journey left them very tired.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 3.9548816680908203, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3006722639531305, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5589124565846606, "dnsmos_bak": 4.126268898543349}
{"id": "nat_156", "text": "The lark sang early in the damp morning.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 3.9382429122924805, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.198866125144129, "dnsmos_sig": 3.530072412299582, "dnsmos_bak": 4.027420230582458}
{"id": "nat_157", "text": "The bees hummed in the tall clover.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.317599296569824, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.242412800191686, "dnsmos_sig": 3.604461274356582, "dnsmos_bak": 3.952612712107263}
{"id": "nat_158", "text": "The thick ice covered the frozen pond.", "audio_duration_s": 2.043356009070295, "utmos": 4.030159950256348, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4263612242029464, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6682411344902772, "dnsmos_bak": 4.176073720983909}
{"id": "nat_159", "text": "The young deer grazed near the tree line.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 3.731426477432251, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.319665393083572, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5694859654515954, "dnsmos_bak": 4.149285462461303}
{"id": "nat_160", "text": "The heavy rains swelled the quiet river.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 4.312939167022705, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2618853706295665, "dnsmos_sig": 3.560389595737679, "dnsmos_bak": 4.008512463660567}
{"id": "nat_161", "text": "The steep cliff dropped to the blue sea.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 4.1507182121276855, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2499507901331275, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5069977926180416, "dnsmos_bak": 4.138374257875786}
{"id": "nat_162", "text": "The bright sparks flew from the anvil.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 3.6878879070281982, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.253840560400987, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5479693036367057, "dnsmos_bak": 4.042084881274159}
{"id": "nat_163", "text": "The cold spring fed the old stone trough.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": 4.142293453216553, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.411320509168825, "dnsmos_sig": 3.666212990204508, "dnsmos_bak": 4.134785644135646}
{"id": "nat_164", "text": "The wild geese flew south at dusk.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.224025726318359, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.247680191972852, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5409413719905873, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0474483791894444}
{"id": "nat_165", "text": "The soft moss covered the old log.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 3.572444438934326, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1644075624519368, "dnsmos_sig": 3.494859948831774, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9858265255154293}
{"id": "nat_166", "text": "The sun shone warm on the stone bench.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.228287696838379, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3445699578213675, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5973164757275806, "dnsmos_bak": 4.121891973746522}
{"id": "nat_167", "text": "The fresh bread smelled good in the kitchen.", "audio_duration_s": 2.182675736961451, "utmos": 3.9994351863861084, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2353954711580633, "dnsmos_sig": 3.489295677956489, "dnsmos_bak": 4.107091543179356}
{"id": "nat_168", "text": "The frog leaped from the muddy bank.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 4.276309490203857, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.0920453128010283, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4175480731862655, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9916490258123005}
{"id": "nat_169", "text": "The tall ship sailed out of the harbor.", "audio_duration_s": 1.8575963718820863, "utmos": 4.296476364135742, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3958868338472343, "dnsmos_sig": 3.631893788210502, "dnsmos_bak": 4.147507704482545}
{"id": "nat_170", "text": "The thick smoke rose from the chimney.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": 4.33234977722168, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2992516398416085, "dnsmos_sig": 3.605315298442106, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0524270917039065}
{"id": "nat_171", "text": "The black cat sat on the warm sill.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 3.662067413330078, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3132352699320626, "dnsmos_sig": 3.561028297821944, "dnsmos_bak": 4.150809390083243}
{"id": "nat_172", "text": "The wide valley lay green and still.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.410477638244629, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.230875697028995, "dnsmos_sig": 3.536591206816921, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0430602473472605}
{"id": "nat_173", "text": "The old well ran dry in late summer.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 3.8408195972442627, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2853451801000495, "dnsmos_sig": 3.565889666012242, "dnsmos_bak": 4.118318633070277}
{"id": "nat_174", "text": "The cold snap froze the small brook.", "audio_duration_s": 2.136235827664399, "utmos": 4.029273509979248, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1809220692230182, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4339440311612455, "dnsmos_bak": 4.094594460525441}
{"id": "nat_175", "text": "The dew dried quickly in the warm sun.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.422149658203125, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.220717437814679, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5301172205848057, "dnsmos_bak": 4.041557281012344}
{"id": "nat_176", "text": "The sharp smell of pine filled the air.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 3.534719467163086, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2450321228530066, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5584177907126087, "dnsmos_bak": 3.99415657946723}
{"id": "nat_177", "text": "The dog barked once and then was still.", "audio_duration_s": 2.507755102040816, "utmos": 3.7150025367736816, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.1704445019164638, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4291979615934083, "dnsmos_bak": 4.109754109996928}
{"id": "nat_178", "text": "The clay jar cracked in the dry heat.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 3.551548957824707, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.092930064915994, "dnsmos_sig": 3.408893389023006, "dnsmos_bak": 4.028286275013453}
{"id": "nat_179", "text": "The loom wove cloth of many colors.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.304482460021973, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.4652593659330555, "dnsmos_sig": 3.7103126192319498, "dnsmos_bak": 4.173242167007176}
{"id": "nat_180", "text": "The brook flowed cold and clear all year.", "audio_duration_s": 2.7399546485260773, "utmos": 3.9742002487182617, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.146608846621638, "dnsmos_sig": 3.515830538299988, "dnsmos_bak": 3.960292204297243}
{"id": "nat_181", "text": "The frost burned the last of the corn.", "audio_duration_s": 1.811156462585034, "utmos": 3.685499668121338, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2166421846612594, "dnsmos_sig": 3.518902004582008, "dnsmos_bak": 4.053473755190635}
{"id": "nat_182", "text": "The long canoe was carved from a log.", "audio_duration_s": 2.089795918367347, "utmos": 4.427247524261475, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.357124232236169, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6443312843681572, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1497561661457905}
{"id": "nat_183", "text": "The roan horse ran best on flat ground.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.234020233154297, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.212684904175646, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5814599432126557, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9378786822551746}
{"id": "nat_184", "text": "The fern grew thick in the dark hollow.", "audio_duration_s": 2.2291156462585033, "utmos": 4.27092170715332, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2538855854036615, "dnsmos_sig": 3.588505162955109, "dnsmos_bak": 4.0395804956543975}
{"id": "nat_185", "text": "The sharp taste of the brine filled his mouth.", "audio_duration_s": 2.3219954648526078, "utmos": 4.343087196350098, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3999451579675326, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6555031324816185, "dnsmos_bak": 4.13047164980646}
{"id": "nat_186", "text": "The cart horse stood still in the rain.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9969160997732427, "utmos": 4.238059997558594, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.118273725060423, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4716143115648985, "dnsmos_bak": 3.8453044195966517}
{"id": "nat_187", "text": "The red brick house faced the park.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9504761904761905, "utmos": 4.107541084289551, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3127870422675016, "dnsmos_sig": 3.552486529381237, "dnsmos_bak": 4.125351314333436}
{"id": "nat_188", "text": "The pale dawn light filled the valley.", "audio_duration_s": 1.7647165532879818, "utmos": 3.6307129859924316, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.271823238367758, "dnsmos_sig": 3.53152913896682, "dnsmos_bak": 4.13757223629873}
{"id": "nat_189", "text": "The dry wood burned hot and fast.", "audio_duration_s": 1.9040362811791383, "utmos": 4.228126525878906, "dnsmos_ovrl": 2.990301767364316, "dnsmos_sig": 3.479881230988837, "dnsmos_bak": 3.6150028241355847}
{"id": "nat_190", "text": "The neural network achieved state-of-the-art performance on the benchmark.", "audio_duration_s": 3.4829931972789114, "utmos": 4.053797721862793, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.395052842611023, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6463924144141355, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1465539869122505}
{"id": "nat_191", "text": "Please confirm your appointment for tomorrow at three o'clock.", "audio_duration_s": 2.8792743764172335, "utmos": 4.340622901916504, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2841113072846904, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6010593677452905, "dnsmos_bak": 4.057521349075563}
{"id": "nat_192", "text": "The quarterly earnings report exceeded analyst expectations by twelve percent.", "audio_duration_s": 4.458231292517007, "utmos": 4.2738037109375, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3998279715504642, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6746321214771265, "dnsmos_bak": 4.147254083838418}
{"id": "nat_193", "text": "We regret to inform you that your flight has been delayed by two hours.", "audio_duration_s": 3.6687528344671203, "utmos": 4.334171772003174, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3385337710425667, "dnsmos_sig": 3.635127834976532, "dnsmos_bak": 4.084054548333889}
{"id": "nat_194", "text": "The temperature today will reach a high of seventy-two degrees Fahrenheit.", "audio_duration_s": 3.4829931972789114, "utmos": 4.417402267456055, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2638131541752347, "dnsmos_sig": 3.622535382092003, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9676237496715974}
{"id": "nat_195", "text": "Your order has been shipped and will arrive within three to five business days.", "audio_duration_s": 3.900952380952381, "utmos": 4.212137699127197, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.334912827490617, "dnsmos_sig": 3.6440388367465473, "dnsmos_bak": 3.9913168523869906}
{"id": "nat_196", "text": "The new software update includes several important security patches.", "audio_duration_s": 3.6687528344671203, "utmos": 4.305322647094727, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.407913699949625, "dnsmos_sig": 3.646774983221853, "dnsmos_bak": 4.1677658038361045}
{"id": "nat_197", "text": "Press one for English, press two for Spanish, or stay on the line.", "audio_duration_s": 4.08671201814059, "utmos": 4.374207496643066, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.384780738757669, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5893347766159063, "dnsmos_bak": 4.159370464321039}
{"id": "nat_198", "text": "The meeting has been rescheduled to next Tuesday at two thirty PM.", "audio_duration_s": 4.179591836734694, "utmos": 4.393479824066162, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.2225484736240686, "dnsmos_sig": 3.4548824813047654, "dnsmos_bak": 4.131226368627105}
{"id": "nat_199", "text": "Thank you for calling customer support. How can I assist you today?", "audio_duration_s": 3.6687528344671203, "utmos": 3.9371585845947266, "dnsmos_ovrl": 3.3016065616468753, "dnsmos_sig": 3.5277479096915036, "dnsmos_bak": 4.170066733889428}
